      "date": "2011-07-07 15:35:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a74927b8-a8ae-11e0-bd2a-52540025f9af).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
